title: Monster, The (1925) Lon Chaney.flv
description:
"A great movie and what a Lon Chaney entrance!" - imdb

This is one of Lon Chaney's more comical turns, playing a mad scientist who takes over a looney bin and proceeds to wreak mayhem and havoc. I had a good response to Laugh, Clown, Laugh so here is more Chaney.

Another youtube reseed in flv format. This is absolutely SILENT, you will have to provide your own music.
